Peter Westaway, chief European
economist at  Nomura Holdings Inc. (8604)  in  London , said he has
resigned from the bank.  Westaway, a former Bank of England official, declined to
comment further by telephone today. A spokeswoman for Nomura in
London confirmed his departure, and declined to comment further.  To contact the reporters on this story:
